    <item>
      <title>370亿美元贷款诈骗案中国嫌疑人面临英国调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/chinese-suspects-in-37-billion-loan-fraud-face-uk-investigation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据法院的判决，一对夫妇在中国被指控主导了价值 2625 亿元人民币（377 亿美元）的欺诈案，目前他们正面临英国的调查，调查内容是他们如何在英国建立价值数百万英镑的房地产投资组合。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/chinese-suspects-in-37-billion-loan-fraud-face-uk-investigation</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 09:10:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利的威尔逊表示，股市落后者将迎头赶上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/strategist-who-foresaw-stock-selloff-says-laggards-due-a-catchup</link>
      <description><![CDATA[曾预见到上个月市场调整的摩根士丹利策略师表示，如果周五公布的数据能够进一步证明经济具有韧性，那么落后于美国股市涨势的股票可能会得到提振。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/strategist-who-foresaw-stock-selloff-says-laggards-due-a-catchup</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 09:10:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BNEF：道路石油使用量即将达到峰值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-03/bnef-peak-road-oil-use-approaching-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[电动汽车销量增长可能正在放缓，但公路运输的石油使用量峰值仍在迅速逼近——而且比你想象的要快。彭博新能源财经下游石油团队负责人洪鲁希于 2024 年 8 月 30 日与 Joumanna Bercetche 进行了讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-03/bnef-peak-road-oil-use-approaching-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 09:02:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Illumina 和 Grail 诉讼案败诉，欧盟合并权受挫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/illumina-grail-deal-was-wrongly-probed-by-eu-top-court-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据最高法院的一项裁决，欧盟本不应该对 Illumina Inc. 以 70 亿美元收购癌症检测提供商 Grail Inc. 的交易进行调查，该裁决对欧盟审查更多全球交易的努力造成了重大打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/illumina-grail-deal-was-wrongly-probed-by-eu-top-court-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 07:48:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛将铜价预测下调 5,000 美元，看涨押注已结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/goldman-slashes-copper-forecast-on-softening-chinese-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团 (Goldman Sachs Group Inc.) 退出了对铜的长期看涨头寸，并将 2025 年铜价预测下调近 5,000 美元，理由是中国需求萎缩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/goldman-slashes-copper-forecast-on-softening-chinese-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 04:24:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
